snippet.title: SuperTAG Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
GET SuperTAG NOW for FREE: https://b0ngo.itch.io/supertag

SuperTAG is an online PVP, fast-paced game of Tag played by using physics-based mechanics.
Play Tag with your friends by doing the sickest of jumps. 

(There can be up to 8 players in 1 lobby)

Check out my itch.io page: https://b0ngo.itch.io/
